{
  "page": "Wedding of Lyonel Corbray and Lady Corbray",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>wedding of Lyonel Corbray and Lady Corbray</b> takes places in <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Corbray\" title=\"Lyonel Corbray\">Lyonel Corbray</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Lord of Heart&#39;s Home\">Lord of Heart's Home</a> and head of the impoverished <a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\">House Corbray</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> marries <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">the daughter</a> of a <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a> merchant.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Wedding\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Wedding</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Corbray\" title=\"Lyonel Corbray\">Lyonel Corbray</a>'s wife bore a sickly child who died in infancy, so Lyonel's heir is his brother, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lyn_Corbray\" title=\"Lyn Corbray\">Lyn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After Lyonel's wife finally dies,<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Protector_of_the_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lord Protector of the Vale\">Lord Protector of the Vale</a>, arranges for Lyonel to marry the <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">sixteen-year-old daughter</a> of a merchant from <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Since the bride is of <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">common birth</a>, a staggering dowry is provided by her father.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Wedding\">Wedding</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Wedding\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Petyr departs the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> and travels across the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn_(valley)\" title=\"Vale of Arryn (valley)\">Vale</a> to attend the wedding. <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>, disguised as his supposed daughter \"Alayne Stone\", hopes he will return from <a href=\"/index.php/Gulltown\" title=\"Gulltown\">Gulltown</a> with a fine gown for her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Although he was one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Lords_Declarant\" title=\"Lords Declarant\">Lords Declarant</a> who opposed Petyr's rule, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Benedar_Belmore\" title=\"Benedar Belmore\">Benedar Belmore</a> reconciles with the Lord Protector and attends the wedding.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Anya Waynwood</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Templeton\" title=\"Symond Templeton\">Symond Templeton</a>, two other Lords Declarant, unexpectedly show up for the wedding feast.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Petyr reunites with Sansa at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a>, he reveals that he had been confident of winning Symond to his side. To gain Anya's support, Petyr arranged for her ward, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Hardyng\" title=\"Harrold Hardyng\">Harrold Hardyng</a>, to marry \"Alayne\"; Petyr paid a dowry even larger than that collected by Lord Corbray.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lyonel is reported to be pleased with his new bride.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Lord Corbray remains with his pregnant wife at <a href=\"/index.php/Heart%27s_Home\" title=\"Heart&#39;s Home\">Heart's Home</a> instead of traveling to the Gates of the Moon to attend the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> for the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_of_Winged_Knights\" title=\"Brotherhood of Winged Knights\">Brotherhood of Winged Knights</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Lyonel's landless brother, Ser Lyn, is resentful.<sup id=\"cite_ref-TWOW_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-TWOW-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Attendees\">Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Corbray\" title=\"House Corbray\"><img alt=\"House Corbray.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/20px-House_Corbray.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/30px-House_Corbray.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9f/House_Corbray.svg/40px-House_Corbray.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Corbray\" title=\"Lyonel Corbray\">Lyonel Corbray</a> and his vassals</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">Lady Corbray</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baelish\" title=\"House Baelish\"><img alt=\"House Baelish.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Baelish.svg/20px-House_Baelish.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Baelish.svg/30px-House_Baelish.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Baelish.svg/40px-House_Baelish.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Waxley\" title=\"House Waxley\"><img alt=\"House Waxley.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/House_Waxley.svg/20px-House_Waxley.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/House_Waxley.svg/30px-House_Waxley.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b1/House_Waxley.svg/40px-House_Waxley.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord Waxley (possibly Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmund_Waxley\" title=\"Edmund Waxley\">Edmund Waxley</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Grafton\" title=\"House Grafton\"><img alt=\"House Grafton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/20px-House_Grafton.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/30px-House_Grafton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dc/House_Grafton.svg/40px-House_Grafton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Grafton\" title=\"Gerold Grafton\">Gerold Grafton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lynderly\" title=\"House Lynderly\"><img alt=\"House Lynderly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/97/House_Lynderly.svg/20px-House_Lynderly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/97/House_Lynderly.svg/30px-House_Lynderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/97/House_Lynderly.svg/40px-House_Lynderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Lynderly\" title=\"Jon Lynderly\">Jon Lynderly</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Belmore\" title=\"House Belmore\"><img alt=\"House Belmore.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/20px-House_Belmore.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/30px-House_Belmore.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/40px-House_Belmore.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Benedar_Belmore\" title=\"Benedar Belmore\">Benedar Belmore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Waynwood\" title=\"House Waynwood\"><img alt=\"House Waynwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Waynwood.svg/20px-House_Waynwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Waynwood.svg/30px-House_Waynwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/House_Waynwood.svg/40px-House_Waynwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Anya_Waynwood\" title=\"Anya Waynwood\">Anya Waynwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\"><img alt=\"House Templeton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/20px-House_Templeton.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/30px-House_Templeton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/40px-House_Templeton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Templeton\" title=\"Symond Templeton\">Symond Templeton</a></li>\n<li>petty <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knights\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Landed knights\">landed knights</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Innocence and experience make for a perfect marriage.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>We have had a letter from <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">your father</a>. He is on his way <a href=\"/index.php/Giant%27s_Lance\" title=\"Giant&#39;s Lance\">home</a>, he says, and hopes to see his darling daughter soon. He writes that <a href=\"/index.php/Lyonel_Corbray\" title=\"Lyonel Corbray\">Lyonel Corbray</a> seems well pleased with <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Corbray\" title=\"Lady Corbray\">his bride</a>, and even more so with her dowry. I do hope Lord Lyonel remembers which one he needs to bed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Myranda_Royce\" title=\"Myranda Royce\">Myranda Royce</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_of_Lyonel_Corbray_and_Lady_Corbray&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Catelyn VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\">2.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-6\">2.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-7\">2.7</a></s